// P10.5 — Debug build configuration overlay.
//
// In DEBUG builds `AdsConfig` always returns Google's official test
// unit ids (see `Services/AdsConfig.swift`) regardless of what's in
// `Info.plist`, so this file intentionally does not define any
// `ADUNIT_ID_*` keys. The placeholder values are kept here for parity
// with `Release.xcconfig` so that any future DEBUG-only override
// surface (a custom AdMob test account, a staging unit, etc.) lives
// alongside its release counterpart instead of being scattered across
// build settings dialogs.
//
// Note: Adding this file to the Debug build configurations also
// confirms the xcconfig wiring is correct end-to-end (build settings
// resolve from xcconfig → target → project for both Debug and
// Release).
